@* 快捷鍵設定 Tab — 讓使用者自訂系統快捷鍵組合 *@
@inject IStringLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@inject IJSRuntime JSRuntime
@implements IDisposable

<div class="p-2">

    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">@L["Shortcut.TabHelpText"]</p>

    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(_conflictError))
    {
        <div class="alert alert-warning d-flex align-items-center mb-3 py-2">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-2"></i>
            <span>@_conflictError</span>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-sm ms-auto"
                    @onclick="() => _conflictError = string.Empty"></button>
        </div>
    }

    <div class="shortcut-editor-table">

        @foreach (var item in _shortcutItems)
        {
            var capturedItem = item;
            <div class="shortcut-row @(capturedItem.IsCapturing ? "shortcut-row--capturing" : "")">

                <div class="shortcut-label">
                    <span>@capturedItem.Label</span>
                    @if (capturedItem.CurrentShortcut != capturedItem.DefaultShortcut)
                    {
                        <small class="text-muted ms-2">
                            (@L["Shortcut.DefaultLabel"] @capturedItem.DefaultShortcut)
                        </small>
                    }
                </div>

                <div class="shortcut-display">
                    @if (capturedItem.IsCapturing)
                    {
                        <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark px-3 py-2 capturing-badge">
                            <i class="bi bi-keyboard me-1"></i>@L["Shortcut.PressKey"]
                        </span>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <div class="shortcut-keys-display">
                            @foreach (var part in capturedItem.CurrentShortcut.Split('+'))
                            {
                                <kbd>@part.Trim()</kbd>
                            }
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>

                <div class="shortcut-actions">
                    @if (!capturedItem.IsCapturing)
                    {
                        <GenericButtonComponent Text="@L["Shortcut.ChangeButton"]"
                                                Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineDarkBlue"
                                                OnClick="@(() => StartCapture(capturedItem))" />
                        @if (capturedItem.CurrentShortcut != capturedItem.DefaultShortcut)
                        {
                            <GenericButtonComponent Text="@L["Shortcut.ResetButton"]"
                                                    Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineGray"
                                                        CssClass="ms-1"
                                                    OnClick="@(() => ResetToDefault(capturedItem))" />
                        }
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <GenericButtonComponent Text="@L["Button.Cancel"]"
                                                Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineRed"
                                                OnClick="@(() => CancelCapture(capturedItem))" />
                    }
                </div>

            </div>
        }

        @* ESC — 固定快捷鍵，不可更改 *@
        <div class="shortcut-row shortcut-row--fixed">
            <div class="shortcut-label">
                <span>@L["Shortcut.CloseModal"]</span>
            </div>
            <div class="shortcut-display">
                <div class="shortcut-keys-display"><kbd>Esc</kbd></div>
            </div>
            <div class="shortcut-actions">
                <span class="text-muted small fst-italic">@L["Shortcut.Fixed"]</span>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-top d-flex justify-content-end">
        <GenericButtonComponent Text="@L["Shortcut.ResetAllButton"]"
                                Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineGray"
                                IconClass="bi bi-arrow-counterclockwise"
                                OnClick="@ResetAll" />
    </div>

</div>

@code {
    [Parameter]
    public EmployeePreference? Model { get; set; }

    private readonly EmployeePreference _fallback = new();
    private DotNetObjectReference<ShortcutKeysTab>? _dotNetRef;
    private List<ShortcutItem> _shortcutItems = new();
    private string _conflictError = string.Empty;
    private EmployeePreference? _lastModel;

    // ===== 內部資料類別 =====

    private class ShortcutItem
    {
        public string ActionId      { get; }
        public string Label         { get; }
        public string DefaultShortcut { get; }
        public string CurrentShortcut { get; set; }
        public bool   IsCapturing   { get; set; }

        public ShortcutItem(string actionId, string label, string defaultShortcut, string? currentValue)
        {
            ActionId       = actionId;
            Label          = label;
            DefaultShortcut = defaultShortcut;
            CurrentShortcut = string.IsNullOrEmpty(currentValue) ? defaultShortcut : currentValue;
        }
    }

    // ===== 生命週期 =====

    protected override void OnInitialized()
    {
        _dotNetRef = DotNetObjectReference.Create(this);
    }

    protected override void OnParametersSet()
    {
        // 只在 Model 參照變更時（Modal 重新開啟）才重建清單
        if (Model != _lastModel)
        {
            _lastModel = Model;
            InitializeItems();
        }
    }

    private void InitializeItems()
    {
        var m = Model ?? _fallback;
        _shortcutItems = new List<ShortcutItem>
        {
            new(nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutPageSearch),
                L["Shortcut.OpenPageSearch"].ToString(),
                ShortcutDefaults.PageSearch,
                m.ShortcutPageSearch),

            new(nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutReportSearch),
                L["Shortcut.OpenReportSelector"].ToString(),
                ShortcutDefaults.ReportSearch,
                m.ShortcutReportSearch),

            new(nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutStickyNotes),
                L["Shortcut.OpenStickyNotes"].ToString(),
                ShortcutDefaults.StickyNotes,
                m.ShortcutStickyNotes),

            new(nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutCalendar),
                L["Shortcut.OpenCalendar"].ToString(),
                ShortcutDefaults.Calendar,
                m.ShortcutCalendar),

            new(nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutQuickAction),
                L["Shortcut.OpenQuickActionMenu"].ToString(),
                ShortcutDefaults.QuickAction,
                m.ShortcutQuickAction),
        };
    }

    // ===== 事件處理 =====

    private async Task StartCapture(ShortcutItem item)
    {
        // 取消其他進行中的擷取
        foreach (var i in _shortcutItems)
            i.IsCapturing = false;

        item.IsCapturing = true;
        _conflictError = string.Empty;
        StateHasChanged();

        await JSRuntime.InvokeVoidAsync("startShortcutCapture",
            _dotNetRef, nameof(OnShortcutCaptured), item.ActionId);
    }

    [JSInvokable]
    public void OnShortcutCaptured(string? combo, string actionId)
    {
        var item = _shortcutItems.FirstOrDefault(i => i.ActionId == actionId);
        if (item == null) return;

        item.IsCapturing = false;

        if (combo != null)
        {
            // 衝突偵測
            var conflict = _shortcutItems.FirstOrDefault(i =>
                i.ActionId != actionId &&
                string.Equals(i.CurrentShortcut, combo, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase));

            if (conflict != null)
            {
                _conflictError = string.Format(L["Shortcut.ConflictError"].ToString(), conflict.Label);
            }
            else
            {
                item.CurrentShortcut = combo;
                WriteToModel(actionId, combo);
                _conflictError = string.Empty;
            }
        }

        InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged);
    }

    private async Task CancelCapture(ShortcutItem item)
    {
        item.IsCapturing = false;
        await JSRuntime.InvokeVoidAsync("cancelShortcutCapture");
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    private void ResetToDefault(ShortcutItem item)
    {
        item.CurrentShortcut = item.DefaultShortcut;
        WriteToModel(item.ActionId, null); // null = 使用預設（儲存 null 到 DB）
        _conflictError = string.Empty;
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    private void ResetAll()
    {
        foreach (var item in _shortcutItems)
        {
            item.CurrentShortcut = item.DefaultShortcut;
            WriteToModel(item.ActionId, null);
        }
        _conflictError = string.Empty;
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// 將 combo 寫回 Model（null 表示使用預設，儲存 null 到 DB）
    /// </summary>
    private void WriteToModel(string actionId, string? combo)
    {
        var m = Model ?? _fallback;
        switch (actionId)
        {
            case nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutPageSearch):
                m.ShortcutPageSearch = combo; break;
            case nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutReportSearch):
                m.ShortcutReportSearch = combo; break;
            case nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutStickyNotes):
                m.ShortcutStickyNotes = combo; break;
            case nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutCalendar):
                m.ShortcutCalendar = combo; break;
            case nameof(EmployeePreference.ShortcutQuickAction):
                m.ShortcutQuickAction = combo; break;
        }
    }

    // ===== IDisposable =====

    public void Dispose()
    {
        _dotNetRef?.Dispose();
    }
}
